ProtoDefines:
. "Let $p$ be an odd prime and let $a$ be an integer. Set $$
\left(\frac{a}{p}\right) = \begin{cases} 0 & \textrm{if} \gcd(a,p)
\neq 1 ,\\ +1 & \textrm{if } a \textrm{ is a quadratic residue, and} \\ -1 &
\textrm{if } a \textrm{ is a quadratic nonresidue} . \end{cases} $$ We call
this symbol the \term{Legendre Symbol}."
